  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMjkz/MDAxNzQ1NDE0NDU4MDIy.YZXLY9mj7lRXH2V2D8268UWLQk9DScbZhTLMvs2CeYgg.oVbRC4aOkHl-bFJIniMGlN42lQFVt5C_ltQFNy3KAuIg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250423_222031423.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1050\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMjkz/MDAxNzQ1NDE0NDU4MDIy.YZXLY9mj7lRXH2V2D8268UWLQk9DScbZhTLMvs2CeYgg.oVbRC4aOkHl-bFJIniMGlN42lQFVt5C_ltQFNy3KAuIg.JPEG/KakaoTalk_20250423_222031423.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">고급 스티커로 디자인을 완성하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-38fd49b8-0904-46a4-8f6f-45001bd9360b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7efa9258-90fe-4378-9028-7cea6f9b3d71\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-64993647-96f6-4c82-a2b5-4eeb50bd48b8\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-64993647-96f6-4c82-a2b5-4eeb50bd48b8\", \"link\": \"https://wedesignpaper.com/gmund\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://wedesignpaper.com/gmund\" target=\"_blank\"><b>https://wedesignpaper.com/gmund</b></a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0d1041c-e7eb-4c2f-92e8-8cb38d7ae082\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe6a803a-3770-43f1-b408-39ec9830dacf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f2b0b6a7-ffc7-4428-82c5-b763f8332c5b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>그문드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 종이는 독일에서 탄생한 가장 오래된 지업사 브랜드 중에 하나입니다. 인쇄 발색은 물론 독창적인 패턴 모양까지 최고급 사양의 용지로 각광받고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-779bf44a-2a7e-45df-84db-24328e11194d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42cdf6d0-2d87-4836-a2ee-f9d71db895f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69cc1ff6-b290-496b-a9cc-11bcda363e6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9761da5-5d05-4d32-9505-13b06e565d13\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그중에 스티커는 고급 와인병에 붙이는 제품으로 사용되며 또는 수제 쿠키 등 고급 브랜드 포장재로도 널리 활용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4bc3cae-079d-4a75-8d3b-f34b8387a52e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06294bfc-95f6-44f8-b864-4593117d0e04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0353d881-d2c9-430d-8bf7-b8f260629b61\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-804f978f-71b5-4990-8502-64ec076dcd23\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그문드 스티커로 제작할 때는 반드시 단가 대비 활용성을 높이기 위해 가장 패턴 모양이 잘 살 수 있는 디자인을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16554512-dd43-45be-9bf5-cee1a12eaa65\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8c358f9-13e1-4b45-9b23-707b491fcc54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6bcd6d2a-f523-4e04-8fe6-32cd86b92ab2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:688px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6bcd6d2a-f523-4e04-8fe6-32cd86b92ab2\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfODgg/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MDA5NDEy.uL69_zzUqpxv9cU9dVP_EBBNS_uEpcs7M-SuNmd20NMg.gXXi8SS9M16f8eN8cDnZH-7zKPWVxh4bwOrDTXLYYqUg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"688\", \"originalHeight\" : \"688\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfODgg/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MDA5NDEy.uL69_zzUqpxv9cU9dVP_EBBNS_uEpcs7M-SuNmd20NMg.gXXi8SS9M16f8eN8cDnZH-7zKPWVxh4bwOrDTXLYYqUg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77e16d9f-1e87-44c9-ae25-e36fc2730e42\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80f104db-e6ca-4212-a5bc-6fd89c820a04\" style=\"\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-80f104db-e6ca-4212-a5bc-6fd89c820a04\", \"link\": \"http://www.chelseawardart.com/wine-cult-wine-labels.html\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"http://www.chelseawardart.com/wine-cult-wine-labels.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chelseawardart.com/wine-cult-wine-labels.html</a></span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9eab2c6b-45f3-4f0c-b6e9-5f8f8d5276f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:438px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9eab2c6b-45f3-4f0c-b6e9-5f8f8d5276f8\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMTQx/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MDM2MDk5.tNXpId_JSqi4IkchcyElDCM-KoPv0yJzQlCwWf7QD5Mg.LDVseMsocrQ-kHF-0EkU_HkgbzP9wOihFSzc3zc5tbwg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"438\", \"originalHeight\" : \"361\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMTQx/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MDM2MDk5.tNXpId_JSqi4IkchcyElDCM-KoPv0yJzQlCwWf7QD5Mg.LDVseMsocrQ-kHF-0EkU_HkgbzP9wOihFSzc3zc5tbwg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e9ed14d7-fe2c-4ec8-8fd0-4592e9a1f690\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2202a041-2a4f-4f0f-8b63-0fe3ede9044a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d5426bba-0a06-479b-9ca7-0a777764f188\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자세히 보시면 휘라레지 처럼 깊은 굴곡의 패턴이 있고 인쇄 시에도 은은하게 패턴 모양이 살아있어서 레트로 감성의 은은한 디자인과 가장 잘 어울린다고 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b914ee09-6d34-48c9-8c83-c0eadf716fe5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-78a209e2-d3bb-4811-8111-17d6b98ebea3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2c16388-7639-49c9-a568-48a46bfcb934\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d2c16388-7639-49c9-a568-48a46bfcb934\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMTQ4/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MjE5NzY0.wdoaihtMVqim2rpabN4pCKm0cXUfEHDteN-W20fXHm0g.kLYbgC_VJrquaeGJbhu-9EkK_tus3z359LP_EMyHsxwg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"919\", \"originalHeight\" : \"554\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA0MjNfMTQ4/MDAxNzQ1NDE1MjE5NzY0.wdoaihtMVqim2rpabN4pCKm0cXUfEHDteN-W20fXHm0g.kLYbgC_VJrquaeGJbhu-9EkK_tus3z359LP_EMyHsxwg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3328a4e-91cf-4a99-a575-727dba5734c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8891f0dc-d725-4e61-b142-d56b9a5b0544\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5241337b-a41d-4ee0-8eab-75def74689f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 감성의 풍경이 들어간 와인병 디자인이 있다면 그문드스티커를 활용하여 제작하시면 가장 퀄리티 높은 효과를 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d4c77eef-5815-4f9b-b90a-66cf7faf91b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0696301-fa32-49e6-b3d6-2de2f070831c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-549c4952-9478-447f-9345-bd2e5a3859da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-522e4564-b39f-4e60-906f-035e7e69eda4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">옛 감성의 풍경이 메인 테마로 디자인되어 있다면 반드시 가장 잘 매칭되는 그문드 스티커를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30302857-6420-448e-b3a9-4d31f6a486c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14855801-64b0-4251-8a55-2e2a26c3c309\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08c6fec1-2bd4-4bdf-8a74-9bec1447b9bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3d9088c-bd76-4c13-a8a8-b5c56ae9c782\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 한 가지 아쉽다면 단가가 높다는 점입니다. 다량으로 제작할 경우 비용이 부담될 수 있습니다. 하지만 소량 다품종의 경우 어느 정도의 퀄리티를 위한 과감한 투자가 좋은 판단일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f604ce8f-f34a-408a-a8e3-4220a516410a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34368382-6d62-4d80-8fe3-3370938c5760\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e00fbc75-59e9-467c-b812-f73cd8091a32\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-acfede54-5bbb-4ed9-972c-89c3ba8fc66e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단가는 최소 작은 사이즈 100장에 3~5만 원 선이라고 생각하시면 됩니다. 장당 300원꼴이라면 무척 비싸지만 수량과 여러 가지 사이즈를 잘 판단해서 500원 미만의 단가로 제작해 보시기 바랍니다. 물론 사각형이 아닌 자유형으로도 제작하여 퀄리티를 높일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e0d44c95-377b-4773-9ccf-616877792046\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3cfa709-787a-4465-a02d-1e1180d01f43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d985d67-3ce2-484a-8660-dc52cb15f226\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fef0a7d6-946a-4580-b96b-f47a7bd4a53c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니에게 디자인을 의뢰하시면 자신의 제품에 맞는 합리적인 가격과 퀄리티를 보장해 드리겠습니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8dfeecf6-8893-42e8-8aa9-012c81db19d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b14a1888-504f-4bf0-a5d2-a791242fed66\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25e3b57c-5971-406b-92fd-6ec99ad1b46d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a29b002c-63de-4838-b015-b7ef8ab34b5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d143efc-f723-4ab2-92f6-7179f2afa43d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bd450a2c-df06-4437-8ebb-0d785eee8c4b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223844312696#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
